reviews: Nothing special but great for the price

I was disappointed with this because the last bra I ordered from this company is my favourite bra. Unfortunately, this one seems like a bigger cup, the fit isn't awful but definitely not proper (even though they are both apparently 34DDD) and the sides of it dig into my armpit no matter how much I adjust the straps. The quality of the bra overall is decent for the price if it weren't for the issues mentioned above.
I am obsessed with this it feels so great, I haven't been able to find mine for a couple days and I'm getting desperate I may order another!

This is great, only cruelty-free deodorant I've tried that actually works and it doesn't irritate my super sensitive skin. I have previously used the Bergamot and Lime one but I prefer this one by far especially because it goes on much easier and smoother. Great smell too that's not overpowering.

I am blown away by how great this face wash is, it takes off all my makeup easily and makes my skin feel incredible. Previously I had bought the Neem Foaming Face Wash but I felt it dried my skin out (I didn't realize it said it was for oily skin) but this Aloe Vera one is incredible for my dry skin.

I love this but not long after getting it noticed it makes a loud sound when drinking through the straw, I have tried unscrewing and re-attaching the straw but nothing seems to help. Also occasionally it seems to leak a bit even if it the lid is on very tightly but this doesn't seem to happen all the time.

I love these and I find they fit true to size but unfortunately, if you wear them a few times between washing, the elastic stretches after you wear them and then start to seem looser and baggy until they are washed again.
It's nice quality but its so long it sticks up way too much unless you fold it so much that it looks equally as ridiculous. it looks like something from a H3H3 video tbh
I'm obsessed with it, Ive had it for over 6 months and it's the best water bottle I've ever had, left it at a friends for a while and he didn't want to give it back because it was so great!

review_title: I've already ordered them twice, love it!
reviews: Such a good deal, these are really great quality and the perfect amount of bouncyness

I want to love this especially because it's so hard to find cruelty free sunscreen but it feels so greasy, I waited a long time between putting it on and doing my makeup yet it still made my foundation go on weird and made my face very shiny, it's an extremely tiny bottle for the price too
It rides up quite a bit but it's cute and not bad for the price :)
I was kind of skeptical that a fairly cheap bra would actually work well but it's amazing! Since it can be hard to find nice inexpensive bras that come in a DDD I'm so glad I got this

review_title: Pretty good but a little bland
reviews: If you like nutritional yeast then you'll probably like this. I used cashew milk and a bit of vegan butter, it turned out pretty good but a bit bland I added some seasoning salt and a couple drops of ketchup and that helped make it much more flavourful. Doesn't taste exactly like Kraft dinner or anything but it's not bad!
Gorgeous, the sewing around the top was a tiny bit wonky but not noticable

review_title: Decent for price but breaks easily
reviews: I loved it at first but the zipper broke twice and by the second time it was unable to be fixed, for the price though it's not bad
